snippet.title: All Hams on Deck! Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download for free on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/all-hams-on-deck/id1447996164
Download for free on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tuna.allhams

All Hams on Deck! is a fast-paced arcade mobile game. Bounce hams, smash melons, and survive as long as possible!

The Bread & Butter Game Co. is an independent game studio based out of Austin, TX.

http://allhamsondeck.com/
http://tbbg.co/
http://twitter.com/tbbgco

The Bread & Butter Jingle was composed by chill_b: https://www.instagram.com/chill_barnard/

Extra special thanks to Dumbest of all Worlds. Please check out their channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC4YNwIa0KQ455Ji2jYVLKFQ

Music credit: Chopstick Slapstick by OurMusicBox: https://youtu.be/3akYklE6r7o
Some sound effects were found on Freesound.org and used a CC Attribution License; those sound effects can be found here:
https://freesound.org/people/cetsoundcrew/sounds/397662/ - CETSoundCrew - whip crack B.wav
http://freesound.org/people/CGEffex/sounds/98341/ - CGEffex - Punch, slap, n’ kick.wav
https://freesound.org/people/juskiddink/sounds/140867/ - Juskiddink - Boing.wav
